        id: "alembic-revision",
        fn: "Alembic revision — write a safe online migration",
        desc: "Add a NOT NULL column with a default to a large table without locking it: split the change into add-nullable, backfill, then enforce NOT NULL — the three-step pattern that survives at scale.",
